Head 1.2 times as long as wide, weakly shiny to dull, polished punctured; frons with coarse, deep and dense punctures (distance between punctures 0.3–1.8 times puncture diameter); malar area rugulose-punctate; vertex, temple and occiput with fine to coarse, superficial and sparse to rather dense punctures (distance between punctures 1.0–3.0 times puncture diameter);occipital margin weakly concave (
Fig. 6
