Fig. 5
); antenna 0.8 times as long as length of fore wing; A 3 3.4 times as long as wide; A 4 4.8 times as long as maximum depth, and 1.4 times as long as length of A 3 (
Fig. 9
); A 5 5.2 times as long as wide, and 1.5 times as long as A 3 (
Fig. 9
